cdata.name: CryptoJacks
cdata.desc: CryptoJack is a PoW/PoS hybrid cryptocurrency focused on online gambling. CryptoJack's ICO extends over a 36 round period in which 10000000 coins will be sold, giving a total of 360000000 Coins being sold on the ICO. CJ uses the X13 algorithm for PoW and SHA-256for PoS block hashing
